      <hr />
      <h3>CONTENT DESIGNATOR HISTORY</h3>
      <div class="history">
         <div>
            <p>In the serials specifications, only subfield $a was defined for field 130
            prior to 1980. The other subfields were defined in 1980. Data appropriate for these
            subfields in records created prior to that time may not be separately subfield
         coded.</p>
         </div>
      </div>
